reviewText:
Not worth the time.
Nothing positive - only the fact I got it for free...
Only negative:
interface is horrible;
can't remap the keys;
no attack on direction or attack on mouse over so you have to click each running enemy separately;
too much text when essential parts take like 1 or 2 lines.
leveling takes a lot of grinding - for example I expected to gain atleast 1 level from clearing the starting zone around base but nope, you have to grind like 100-200 monsters before you get to second level.
